Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&\i1}Bác Yaguchi ngáy kinh khủng quá!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}ZZZZZZZ...
